Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:10.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.18,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:38.14,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Gel Magic: Sticky Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:41.27,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:45.94,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this, Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:48.66,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:52.22,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who will destroy the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:00.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:05.71,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:07.33,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:10.84,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King, Julius Novachrono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:11.96,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:16.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:17.93,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.06,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been too difficult \Nwith your numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:25.98,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? I'll let one of you \Nsurvive, so why not surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:27.90,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be first come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.56,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:38.24,italics,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,How is he moving like that?!\NI can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:40.27,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:42.74,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to handle these numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:47.44,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Time Binding Magic: Chrono Stasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:52.25,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.75,italics,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:55.76,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,...at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.58,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was able to restrain all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.76,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Were you more worn out than I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:03.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:05.27,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:09.02,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We seem to be connected by fate somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:14.65,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become the \NWizard King someday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:19.41,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, watch carefully \Nand don't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:24.41,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This is only a small fraction \Nof what you'll have to surpass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.94,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's blinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is this light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:06.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:11.08,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:15.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:20.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.34,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.93,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.93,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:34.94,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.44,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:42.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:47.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:53.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:56.46,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:00.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.84,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:07.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.56,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Light
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:27.66,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:30.66,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He took all of his little friends back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:35.87,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Light magic that's faster than my own... \NI wonder if that was the enemy's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:40.14,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He seems interesting... I mean, formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:41.69,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.84,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to keep one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.75,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.01,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:52.69,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there, Marx.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:58.88,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. I've been a bit busy, \Nso I blocked the communication spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:02.99,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Please hurry\Nto the medical ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.26,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon... Leopold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.03,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they wake up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.01,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:33.31,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,We've strengthened the magic barrier \Nand repaired the communication spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.93,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,We've gathered more Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.18,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,and are having them scout \Nevery inch of the town
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.40,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,to ensure no enemies remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:41.42,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the royal capital is fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:46.99,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,We're also looking for that awfully loud—\Ner, lively Black Bulls boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't die so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.74,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Asta. I'm going to \Npunch you when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.82,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.25,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone. Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.01,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.27,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, guys. Looks like you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.63,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:16.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I thought I was done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! It's because you're always so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you learned your lesson, Stupidsta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.75,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:30.19,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:33.09,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm so glad you came back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:36.78,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were dead. I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:41.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... Thanks for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:44.29,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to punch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:46.26,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:50.19,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I was so, so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.14,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.72,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:02.95,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how strong Fuegoleon is, \Nwe don't know when he'll wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.85,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That was a miscalculation on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:10.27,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,No, this was due to our inexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:15.49,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,We've confirmed that the pendant \NFuegoleon was wearing is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.17,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Pendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.75,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be what they were after?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.67,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.94,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,From what they said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.26,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,they appear to be a terrorist group \Nwith a grudge against the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.07,flashback,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.76,flashback,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who will destroy the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.11,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't seem to be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:42.77,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The jewels embedded into that stone slab...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:47.02,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Was Fuegoleon's pendant a part of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.34,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It had several holes \Nthat were still empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.53,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but what happens when \Nthey gather all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:58.04,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,There is the possibility that Fuegoleon \Nwas targeted because of his pendant,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.45,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but there's also a high possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:05.54,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,that his strength and ideals \Nwould've gotten in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.57,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I've been investigating \Nvarious dissidents in secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.30,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,and this is the first time \NI've picked up their trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:17.30,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that they were planning \Nsomething that extraordinary and powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.54,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have left the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.67,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get the details from our captive later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.31,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.74,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,people look to the\NMagic Knights for one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.65,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Peace in the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.57,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In order to preserve that, we'll keep \Nfighting with everything we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.83,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.27,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is that guy's problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:48.59,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be showing solidarity \Nright now. Take the hint, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.12,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Has the enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:54.09,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,awakened not a sleeping lion, \Nbut a sleeping hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.34,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.06,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,What an appalling spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.88,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Never let this happen again, Nozel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:07.60,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,And Fuegoleon, I will find \Nthe scum who did this to you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.75,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,and slay them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:18.50,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I never feel this useless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.21,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.03,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,We shall become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:24.43,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.12,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll become the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.59,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be resting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:35.16,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! I'm relieved that \Nwe both pulled through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:40.51,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,As my rival who has faced death \Nwith me, you must also get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.27,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I will surpass my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:47.31,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be the next Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.77,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.03,flashback,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.76,flashback,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,what is that mark on your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.78,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:05.29,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,This mark is handed down in the Vermillion \Nfamily as a sign of a personal oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:09.29,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,It's worn only by those prepared to \Nconquer themselves and become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.96,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,This... is the mark of my oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:22.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I don't really get it, but it looks \Nlike you're worthy to be my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So... who the heck are you, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.48,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.54,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,How?! How could you still not know who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I only remember people who \Nproperly introduce themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.45,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I am Leopold Vermillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.56,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be friends, \Nso call me Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:38.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're moving way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.85,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:47.45,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King concluded that \Nthe attack on the royal capital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.75,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,had been the work of \Nanti-Clover Kingdom terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:55.50,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He declared his intent to continue \Nresolutely opposing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and the masses were fully supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's invasion was enabled by
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:06.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the disappearance of some of the mages who \Nmaintained the capital's magic barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:11.10,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Had the enemy done away\Nwith them, or had they defected?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:19.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This fact was not made public,\Nbut the Wizard King was sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.28,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:26.74,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but there's a traitor among the \Nmages in the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:42.84,sign_16757_180_Interrogation_Ro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(965,1)}Interrogation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:42.84,top,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.85,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,There's some kind of protection on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.71,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't search for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:53.09,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there wasn't, we'd never talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.62,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Our master is the light in the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:58.36,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,He's our god!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:03.37,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only one who hasn't abandoned us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.62,main,Geork,0000,0000,0000,,We will never betray him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:19.63,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, their master has some absolute\Nunifying force and fearsome magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:24.96,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I'm assuming the one who defeated \NCaptain Fuegoleon is also their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.89,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:30.89,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,When he wakes up, we may learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:35.25,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Let us wait for the Lion King to awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.02,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.07,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.86,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.69,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,They hurt. They hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.37,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.58,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid little brat Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.87,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill him, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:58.09,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to gather the \Nultimate army of the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.08,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,That anti-magic kid, Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:04.24,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill him, Rades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:08.54,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tinker with him \Nwhile he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:09.55,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:12.64,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I already \Ntreated your wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.93,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no way they'd still be hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.92,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! They still ache!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:20.75,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that brat first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.82,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hands off, Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.13,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Can't hear you, can't hear you,\Ncan't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.89,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I see you again soon, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:40.09,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,For the next time I see you, Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:44.59,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the little samples \NI got while you were in the gel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.74,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,and research and research!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.85,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't save Geork and Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:59.86,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have big egos, \Nbut they worship you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:03.06,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,They won't give them any information on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.11,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:10.49,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're alive, I will\Nsave them, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:23.18,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had dodged it, but I seem \Nto have taken a little of the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:28.81,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that accelerates \Ntime... and drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.64,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King... As expected, \Nhe has phenomenal power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:42.90,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But we will build up our \Nstrength and defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:56.26,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get our revenge and establish \Na new country that will be ours alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.04,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mister and Miss Magic Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.25,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.55,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I just did the obvious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.05,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is to thank you. I made them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.36,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:21.43,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.38,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:30.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...are you here, Charmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:35.49,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Where the nummy things are,\Nthere I shall be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.79,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.51,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La? La?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, she gave those to {\i1}us{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.30,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. They're delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't mind having one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise. It's actually good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in an unusually good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.22,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I had a fateful encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.79,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably too young to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how did you get into the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:15.95,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:22.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:26.13,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Is her magic actually really amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:29.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.23,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's Asta and Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.32,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:42.73,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Have your wounds fully healed?\NI asked you that before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:46.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, like I said before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:52.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, I heard you took down the enemy \Nlike it was nothing, you jerkface!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Jerkface?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.99,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My meal-saving prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuno! Greet me properly, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you know my prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get a big head just \Nbecause you took one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:08.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Courtesy makes the world go round!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.05,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.85,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was that too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.83,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, Yuno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:49.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is he stupid?! Was he \Nactually trying to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:55.84,sign_25699_273_See_ya__Shrimpst,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(502,1)}See ya, Shrimpsta
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.25,italicstop,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Shrimpsta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling "Shrimpsta," \NYuno, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come down here and fight me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:04.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot something like that \Njust so you can write magic letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:07.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare ignore me and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.23,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the ferocious storm of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:13.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring me is the worst thing you could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.59,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:20.06,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's magic has gotten much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.87,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What could've happened in \Nsuch a short amount of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:27.87,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.03,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:33.98,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,so the next time we meet, I'll be\Nable to fight alongside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.88,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,And then... And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:46.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll just have to fight \Nwhen we both get a lot stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.29,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:53.65,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The stronger you become, \NI'll get even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:59.65,sign_27240_290_Black_Bulls__Bas,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Black Bulls' Base
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:59.65,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Magna, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:03.06,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so exhausted from my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:03.99,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,So tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:06.06,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.37,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We got recognized for our \Ndeeds and got a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.71,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:12.71,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Not so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:17.01,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Our combo attack, the Crackling Magna\NTyphoon, was amazing, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.55,sign_25699_273_See_ya__Shrimpst,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Crackling Magna Typhoon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.55,top,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We're never doing that move again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.55,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're all back safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:27.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna keep on showing the \Nother Black Bulls how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:32.31,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, my time has arrived! \NMake sure you keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:35.82,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They were so impressed with what I did \Nduring all the trouble at the capital
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:44.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,that they made me a third-class junior \NMagic Knight at a special awards ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.85,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:50.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's a third-class \Njunior Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.33,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:57.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Have you guys been Magic Knights all \Nthis time without knowing what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Magic Knight rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And since you guys haven't \Nchanged since you all joined,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,you're still fifth-class Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Better start showing Asta some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.60,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.60,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And by the way, Charmy became \Na first-class junior Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.36,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,On your knees, inferiors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.46,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:23.99,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you follow me, you inferiors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:28.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they were impressed that \Nshe captured one of the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks to me like she was just trying \Nto beat her up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:38.15,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Worship me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What's that weird dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.13,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This is somehow very infuriating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:48.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, well done, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain Fuegoleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Fuegoleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:56.90,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're worrying about, punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:01.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That hot-blooded king of seriousness \Nwon't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:04.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he'll come back even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:11.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to train even \Nharder and get stronger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're gonna rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're too injured. You're going\Nto die. Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:19.42,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But you made me do it in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You need to take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:22.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:25.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A break...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A break? You're getting time off, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.30,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's head to a mixer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.31,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A m-mixer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set everything up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:36.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.91,main,Final,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do you wanna come too, Captain Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:06.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:09.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:11.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:16.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:22.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:24.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:27.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:30.66,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:33.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:36.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:38.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:41.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:43.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:46.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:48.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:52.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:58.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:01.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
